data.description: Looking for a new home that offers a serene escape from the world? Look no further! You'll be delighted by the picturesque park-like backyard of this property, complete with stunning views of a private lake. This home is full of wonderful features, including an updated master bath with new tile, paint, and shower. The master suite is a true oasis, with a beautiful view of the backyard and a cozy sitting area. The living room is warm and inviting, with beautiful flooring, newer paint, and a cozy fireplace. The kitchen is a cook's dream, with granite counters and a breakfast bar. Serve up your culinary creations in the spacious dining room, with plenty of natural light. Separated from the master, you'll find two nice-sized guest bedrooms and a full bath with new paint. Upstairs, there's a spacious bedroom that could also serve as a playroom or office, complete with a walk-in closet and lots of extra storage space in the walk-in attic. Boasting a large 2car garage, it's the perfect home!
